# Production-Grade Hackathon Backend with Authentication & RBAC

A comprehensive Node.js/Express backend featuring Drizzle ORM with PostgreSQL, multi-method authentication (JWT, sessions, OAuth), and role-based access control.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Database Setup**: You'll need a PostgreSQL database running locally or a hosted instance (e.g., Supabase, Neon, Railway). Please confirm your preferred setup.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **OAuth Providers**: To enable Google and GitHub OAuth, you'll need to create OAuth apps and provide the client IDs and secrets. I can set up the code structure, and you can add credentials later.

